description: G.f. satisfies A(x) = 1 + x*cycle_index(G,A(x)) where G = tetragonal pyramid group of order 8 with cycle index (A1^5+2*A1*A4+3*A1*A2^2+2*A1^3*A2)/8.
references: B. A. Kennedy et al., Group theory and isomerism, Inorg. Chem. 3 (1964), 265-268, for cycle index.
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_.
